				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\langle {O}_{i,0},{O}_{i,1},\ldots ,{O}_{i,23}\rangle $$\end{document}. These are used as an input to the energy use models. Synthetic household member activity scheduling conflicts are handled in the activity model.

